"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>昂坪360<br />\nSky100<br />\n蠟像館</blockquote><br />\n大多你迪士尼<br />\n窮撚那有錢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9623d418d3fd015d98c569892e50283f1720edb0","tid":424803,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:46:02.000Z","msg":"細個好多都去過<br />\n大左無再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4109f597a4abec4bb1d0a498c57b15be90be8c","tid":424803,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:46:43.000Z","msg":"新界未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6e086a425d2c24bfb37bb25278f9be3c853c59","tid":424803,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"明明為你都係得3x<br />\n點解咁快用成世人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95f7375bbd9d1d440d1e56ad2aa6f7ca9578b42","tid":424803,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:01:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新界未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機場都未去過，<br />\n咁慘?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718b3af96444be100442b0dd04192d695d5f43cb","tid":424803,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新界未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機場都未去過，<br />\n咁慘?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能對上一次係香港啟德機場"}]}